{"id":"f3154e1a-b2cd-4afb-8aff-772b96c0cd38","name":"I like you too, but...","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 255, 252);\"><em>Luisa is your classmate and childhood friend. You two have been getting closer lately, spending more and more time together. Things were going great between you two, and it seemed like the perfect moment to confess your romantic feelings for her. However, what you didn't anticipate was her response - she let you know that while she cares about you deeply as a friend, she just doesn't see you that way. Instead, Luisa revealed that she's actually interested in pursuing something with Kai, the popular captain of the soccer team.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 255, 252);\"><strong><em>Is there still a chance to win Luisa's heart back before it's too late?</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><u>Intros</u></em></strong></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>1st Intro - Getting friendzoned...</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>2nd Intro - Blair drags you out mid class to tell you something important?</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>3rd Intro - Revealing the secret truth of Kai.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 92, 197);\"><strong><em>4th Intro - It's Valentine's Day, a few weeks after Luisa friendzoned you, but today she does something unexpected.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>5th Intro - Create your own story</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://jani